=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>This time I drop 400 hp's instead of 1200. I am at FM because I only stunned with my DW bracer. Four right clicks of my helm and I am at 100% again. <br><br>What a difference !<br><br>So then I get foolish and chase down a Frost Giant Scout, did I mention I run pretty fast when I am just about dead?<br><br>Anyways..I stun (try) him once to pull him in  and when I am at 50% health he is still at 60% or so.<br><br>Again before the change I would 20% ish on health and he would be 80% ....so that was cool.<br><br>I am a level 47 HEF Paladin.<br><br>I hunt in Rathe to make pp to buy goodies, so I am not a twink.<br><br>I love to hear about level 60's and thier uber stats, but I have never seen a real-time story for us mid guys.<br><br>I really hope this helps....<br><br>BUY AC !!!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Kassel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utorrast.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Torrast</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/21/02 3:02:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14987.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AC vs Stats revisited...not an equipment check :)</span><hr size=1> It depends on the stat gain vs ac loss.  I recently lost 11ac, but gained 10str, 5wis, 9dex, 10cr and 10dr.  Being on a pvp server, this is a better setup. <p>Torrast Trueblade<br>Whining Knight of the White Rose<br><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=10966>Garbage</a><br><a href=http://www.mage